Drop-in replacement for JBoss TreeCache and PojoCache powered by Terracotta. This is a Terracotta Integration Module (TIM) for Terracotta Cache, a distributed cache that is API-compatible with the JBoss PojoCache and TreeCache components. If you are currently using one of these components, you can replace the use of those components with Terracotta Cache and only minimal code changes.
